<p class="">If the right hon. Gentleman for very good reasons happens to be absent, as is frequently the case, are we to understand that the Questions should be addressed to the Deputy Prime Minister, who is Deputy Minister of Defence?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
